===Adjective===
{{en-adj|craz|ier}}

# Continuously and permanently infatuated with someone; consistantly experiencing intense feelings of attraction and affection which make it very challenging to pay attention to or focus on anything other than the person for whom they care so much for. These feelings are often induced by someone who combines excessive amounts of natural beauty with extremely incredible personality traits in a manner completely unfair to the rest of the world.

Example: Jared is '''crazy''' about Josslyn.

